{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Tax rebate for those who worked during the pandemic in their place of work",
        "additional_details": "I think everyone who went into work during the pandemic should be rewarded for continuing to work at their place of work and helping keep the country functioning. Our taxes helped pay for the Government furlough scheme so why can't we have some back?",
        "background": "I want the Government to arrange a tax rebate for those who had to go into work during the pandemic; those of us who were not furloughed and could not work from home due to the nature of our jobs.",
